{"tid":2231523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同阿媽相處好攰","createTime":"2020-10-05T17:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T04:59:21.000Z","uid":264067,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04c7e8e69047aba79968aad633e5d28ca8f35a09","tid":2231523,"uid":264067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:06:19.000Z","msg":"其實我真係錫我呀媽，但唔知點解對住佢有莫名嘅煩躁感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時係會關心佢，見佢病又會問佢，又會叫佢去睇醫生，但當佢一出聲，我就覺得好煩，我就會開始hea 答，佢之後就話我唔關心佢。<br />\n<br />\n我見其他人同阿媽出街有講又笑，但我同阿媽出街就會覺得好攰，連應佢嘅氣力都冇，但當分開行又會正常返。點解會係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55d7a18e5d9c0a266f80917d87f7172de3e8479","tid":2231523,"uid":341236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣"},{"pid":"0d080fa37be63c2abcf4ee716124d9467f34b1ef","tid":2231523,"uid":311566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"同老母出街好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866a50b12cfb0483d602aa6ab222bc7f4a34802a","tid":2231523,"uid":264067,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"其實好想同佢打好關係，但佢一出聲我就開始覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解會咁？好想戒左呢個心態"},{"pid":"94d575931baf8e5d0f0e18259177cc766c91cd4d","tid":2231523,"uid":142313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"866a50b12cfb0483d602aa6ab222bc7f4a34802a","tid":2231523,"uid":264067,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"其實好想同佢打好關係，但佢一出聲我就開始覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解會咁？好想戒左呢個心態"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"慣左 我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大都係呢種態度好難改<br />\n係聽到把聲或者見到個人已經有呢種情緒反射出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71085d7fcd48af2c46a04a77ab3a6a66ee4b0151","tid":2231523,"uid":223912,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢一問我嘢我就燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddac4df740aef96e912c303f84c3d96008414ba","tid":2231523,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:24:38.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣"},{"pid":"428dd5557af5dd40168df913722b9c8ff1ec89aa","tid":2231523,"uid":82717,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"我平日無咩脾氣 但同佢相處會好忟憎 同佢溝通真係幾攰<br />\n我阿媽理解能力好差 聽野就聽一半 <br />\n佢成日唔覺唔覺係度放負 <br />\n我聽落去覺得佢成日搬是非"},{"pid":"184e759ed144d9b798b9c084f6f1fb2e9e22e3d0","tid":2231523,"uid":106568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:24:17.000Z","msg":"之前都係咁 而家覺得好後悔<br />\n媽媽前日過左身 好後悔自己之前咁樣 明明可以對佢好d <br />\n講野既語氣可以好d 可以對佢更加有耐性 但都冇咁做到<br />\n唔好等失去先黎後悔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bd07387a7e419f32ecd9cd2354acd070639833","tid":2231523,"uid":264067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"184e759ed144d9b798b9c084f6f1fb2e9e22e3d0","tid":2231523,"uid":106568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:24:17.000Z","msg":"之前都係咁 而家覺得好後悔<br />\n媽媽前日過左身 好後悔自己之前咁樣 明明可以對佢好d <br />\n講野既語氣可以好d 可以對佢更加有耐性 但都冇咁做到<br />\n唔好等失去先黎後悔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"唔通人要失去先學識珍惜....但我唔想，我好想對我呀媽好啲，心態係時候要變下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢一問野我又開始覺得煩咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb578d1b3be476a49e9d4c245ee7bbae6799e60","tid":2231523,"uid":23431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n其實我內心係好愛佢<br />\n但唔知點解好唔想同佢兩個人出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca5ec3107e0d58ffca2852e467744ac93cd43ae","tid":2231523,"uid":320293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}